# Studio Settings

Current settings for **<%= @current_studio.name %>**:

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Name | <%= @current_studio.name %> |
| Handle | <%= @current_studio.handle %> |
| Description | <%= @current_studio.description || "(none)" %> |
| Timezone | <%= @current_studio.timezone %> |
| Tempo | <%= @current_studio.tempo %> |
| Synchronization Mode | <%= @current_studio.synchronization_mode %> |
<% if @current_tenant.api_enabled? %>
| Invitations | <%= @current_studio.all_members_can_invite? ? 'All members can invite' : 'Only admins can invite' %> |
| Representation | <%= @current_studio.any_member_can_represent? ? 'Any member can represent' : 'Only representatives' %> |
| File Uploads | <%= @current_studio.allow_file_uploads? ? 'Enabled' : 'Disabled' %> |
| API Access | <%= @current_studio.api_enabled? ? 'Enabled' : 'Disabled' %> |
<% end %>
