## [Actions](<%= @current_studio.path %>/settings/actions)

* [`update_studio_settings(name, description, timezone, tempo, synchronization_mode, invitations, representation, file_uploads, api_enabled)`](<%= @current_studio.path %>/settings/actions/update_studio_settings) - Update studio settings
